Title: Professionally Equipped
Description:
Say, I heard from Haephesta that you're a working artisan as well.

We'd like to get you set up with some professional equipment. Free of charge. That's what business partners are for, right?

Talk to our tailor, Mahra Treebender, to get fitted.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak to Mahra Treebender at the Ruby Lifeshrine.

Objectives.Text: Wait for Mahra to Craft Your Gear
